commit.message: okay okay for real this time...last submit.
Some polish items on the MapActivity.

Merge branch 'master' of https://github.com/lsftw/AmISafe

Conflicts:

Added Color gradient functionality to the activity bar.

Fixed bug with map activity not starting from startup. Also, fixed issue
with SQLite query, and changed the static function to return a List
instead of a primitive array.
Commit it so I can test it.

Added Crime object class to be used to extract crimes from the database.
Additionally, the CrimeIncidents class is a static class that is used to
instantiate the database as well as to receive information from the
database using the "getNearbyCrimes" method.
Added more functionality stuff for buttons (From/To locations)

Moved the database functionality out of this class. Static classes
associated with the database will be committed later.
Made a minor fix to my previous update.
Updated GUI with some visibility changes for buttons.
fully loaded initial database is populated with crime data from 2014.

Added DatabaseHelper and testing logs in MainActivity for loading db
from file.
Target sdk version match min sdk version, add internet and location permissions.
